{"tid":1559174,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"多名前官員及學者聯署，要求政府嚴肅制止執法人員使用不必要武力。","createTime":"2019-09-10T16:45:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T17:19:27.000Z","uid":58335,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2287d0b12b9b51fc359149510e0d6f5876368d5b","tid":1559174,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:45:37.000Z","msg":"聯署的包括前運房局副局長邱誠武、前商經局副局長梁敬國、總商會總裁袁莎妮、學者如林本利、關焯照以及袁天佑等多名牧師，他們指近日警方頻頻出現不必要的武力，違反基本法對市民的人身安全的保障，亦令警隊的文明形象蒙污蒙羞，懇請政府正視問題，馬上嚴肅制止執法人員使用不必要武力，亦呼籲示威的市民停止對公共建設造成破壞。<br />\n<br />\n而為了釋除民眾不平，聯署人同時懇請政府盡快徹查7月21日的元朗衝突，亦應把8月31日太子站衝突事件完整地公開交待，政府亦應成立獨立調查委員會，積極回應主流民意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=362332&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D362332%26refer%3D&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeReqf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=e39ed46d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D362332%26refer%3D&h=d48bc6f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=362332&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"5154493ba970801f153309bd9f961cc20d460dc3","tid":1559174,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:09:24.000Z","msg":"軍警政府 算吧啦"},{"pid":"1b91029775a777e1692650098aa1abc0c34071e8","tid":1559174,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:12:24.000Z","msg":"sorry 借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻煩未食飯既同我入哂黎!!! 唔準有人餓住個肚!!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《急推》 前線唔好餓死呀<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1540938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1540938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bc6f37f849af0fd089d5aa7e086d9e6530d92c2b","tid":1559174,"uid"